=\"hkgmoji\" /> 機會黎啦飛雲"},{"pid":"3b6522989f72f9e78d2a287f2389b5eb4536fd64","tid":168872,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d55e68f6b0b70f3ffcc59ecc9bddddf4f90390","tid":168872,"uid":88371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:16:18.000Z","msg":"算吧啦 如果''靚'' 係認真高質果隻靚<br />\n而又唔係誇張地矮<br />\n你睇下到埋牙果時佢地點簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ac463c76c4f2901a0ef16a21395375ba3241fc","tid":168872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19968626&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19968626%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170324&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3b33f6d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19968626%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170324&h=c921714b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19968626&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170324</a><br />\n<br />\n其實見到樓主貼啲唔貼啲都知道有啲唔妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n坊間一句「你的樣子如何，你的日子也必如何」，或許引證了不少社會現況，不過日本女大學生似乎另有想法。當要在矮小卻帥氣、以及高大但樣子普通的男生中揀出男友時，大多數日女寧願選擇後者。<br />\n<br />\n有網站訪問了286位女大學生，要她們選擇與「矮小型男」還是「高但樣普通」的男生拍拖，結果有75.2%女生表示會選擇「高男」，顯示樣貌無法取代身高的優勢。<br />\n<br />\n選擇高男的女生都表示：「我有個樣貌普通的男友就夠了」、「長得高好看一點」、「美男子已經夠多了」。<br />\n<br />\n而選擇另一方的女生，卻並單單受帥氣樣貌吸引，她們稱：「我本身很矮所以沒所謂」、「因為我個子不高，要與高佬邊走邊說話很辛苦」等等。<br />\n-----------------<br />\n點解睇落好似係日本妹對靚仔冇安全感？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68450cb98b1a7c01703b3c68d4330106ae48943","tid":168872,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野叫矮小型男<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男仔170以下有資格叫型男咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n矮小型 男"},{"pid":"453b26229ee9c90cdeef5e12d451e560cbcf4965","tid":168872,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"哼，高大哂咩，行街小心撞親個頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e3cc6845e22d8bcd59cac422ef87db134860fd","tid":168872,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜撚野叫矮小型男<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男仔170以下有資格叫型男咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n矮小型 男</blockquote><br />\n日本大把型男偶像 170以下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8e0c5499acc43f12e8056642338a1051836090","tid":168872,"uid":74619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:02:06.000Z","msg":"郭富城做矮靚仔代表 高醜既搵邊個做代表好？"},{"pid":"788239a5e9bc3328296a2d001a3f36bc31acb1af","tid":168872,"uid":8452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為日男普遍真係好矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但去日本見到好多後生既都好撚高喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf58c738f1278fc96005e22996994ee478238423","tid":168872,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>郭富城做矮靚仔代表 高醜既搵邊個做代表好？</blockquote><br />\n香港多數係高醜vs矮靚仔<br />\n佢呢個係普通樣高vs矮靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a150c1cca4640638bf7ccd238dd9119ea84577e","tid":168872,"uid":93903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"去日本旅遊見到啲仔都唔矮 <br />\n女就多數都係矮"},{"pid":"c5e009840ce61f261fc6cd4ffc451de5ad72f7f7","tid":168872,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去日本旅遊見到啲仔都唔矮 <br />\n女就多數都係矮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班女個個著哂高踭鞋都仲係好撚矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,日本女仔平均身高大約150 到"},{"pid":"5482f251f35b7f09cb0668d4cdfd5160d8f8c8d7","tid":168872,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"宜家00後d女仔好睇重身高<br />\n中學好多女仔都鐘意身高差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而80後無咁睇重<br />\n因為果個年代d男仔未有咁高住"},{"pid":"08a4ac0266b0c416256b7fee215eeccb93fbc728","tid":168872,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"女人邊信得過，最後咪又係揀最有錢果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd5f470d21fff7c2c63b77ddae09dc45300e51b","tid":168872,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"又矮又唔型咁點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8460bf6cd441ad94e79a1d1b5fcfb1b3e6258f","tid":168872,"uid":20204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"日子新一代好多好高"},{"pid":"092b2d8b470019872d12491450757502500c1cd9","tid":168872,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:14:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"162f2cab880309ec5b4e7242f5e33664c377f725","tid":168872,"uid":74407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得165點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img